trans-unit.source: The ReplicationNeighbor class contains information about a replication neighbor of an <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainController"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ReplicationNeighbor inneholder informasjon om en replikering nabo for en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainController"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of replication failures since the last successful replication cycle.
trans-unit.target: Henter antall replikering feil etter forrige vellykkede replikering sirkulere.

trans-unit.source: The number of failed replication attempts from this source since the last successful replication attempt.
trans-unit.target: Maksimalt antall mislykkede replikering forsøk fra denne kilden etter forrige vellykkede replikering forsøk.

trans-unit.source: If no previous attempt was successful, the return value is the number of failed replication attempts since the source was added as a neighbor.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen forrige forsøket var vellykket, er returverdien antall mislykkede replikering forsøk fordi kilden er lagt til som en nabo.

trans-unit.source: Gets the time of the last replication attempt from this source.
trans-unit.target: Henter tidspunktet for det siste forsøket på replikering fra denne kilden.

trans-unit.source: The time of the last replication attempt.
trans-unit.target: Tidspunktet for det siste forsøket på replikering.

trans-unit.source: If no replication attempt occurred, the value is zero.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen replikering forsøk oppstod er verdien null.

trans-unit.source: Gets the time of the last successful replication cycle from this source.
trans-unit.target: Henter klokkeslettet for den siste vellykkede replikering syklusen fra denne kilden.

trans-unit.source: The time of the last successful synchronization.
trans-unit.target: Klokkeslettet for den siste vellykkede synkroniseringen.

trans-unit.source: If no replication succeeded, the value is zero.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen replikeringen er fullført, er verdien null.

trans-unit.source: Gets the message that is associated with the last replication attempt from this source.
trans-unit.target: Henter meldingen som er knyttet til det siste forsøket for replikering på fra denne kilden.

trans-unit.source: The message that corresponds to the last replication attempt.
trans-unit.target: Meldingen som tilsvarer den siste forsøk på replikering.

trans-unit.source: If the last attempt succeeded, the value is an empty string.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det siste forsøket på lyktes, er verdien en tom streng.

trans-unit.source: Gets the error code that is associated with the last replication attempt from this source.
trans-unit.target: Henter feilkoden som er knyttet til det siste forsøket for replikering på fra denne kilden.

trans-unit.source: The error code for the last replication attempt.
trans-unit.target: Feilkoden for det siste forsøket på replikering.

trans-unit.source: If the last attempt succeeded, the value is ERROR_SUCCESS.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det siste forsøket på lyktes, er verdien ERROR_SUCCESS.

trans-unit.source: Gets the partition name for this <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter partisjonsnavnet for denne <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The name of the partition for this <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på partisjonen for dette <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the attribute and object settings for this <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter innstillinger for attributtet og objektet for dette <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor.ReplicationNeighborOptions> value that contains the attribute and option settings for this <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor.ReplicationNeighborOptions>verdi som inneholder innstillinger for attributtet og alternativet for dette <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor"> </xref> objektet.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationNeighbor.ReplicationNeighborOptions>

trans-unit.source: Gets the invocation identifier that was used by the replication source server in the last replication attempt.
trans-unit.target: Henter aktiverings-ID som er brukt av replikering kildeserveren i det siste forsøket på replikering.

trans-unit.source: The invocation identifier that was used by the replication source server in the last replication attempt.
trans-unit.target: Aktivering-identifikatoren som er brukt av replikering kildeserveren i det siste forsøket på replikering.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på kildeserveren replikering.

trans-unit.source: The name of the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på kildeserveren replikering.

trans-unit.source: Gets the transport type that was used for replication.
trans-unit.target: Henter transporttypen som ble brukt for replikering.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryTransportType"></xref> enumeration value that indicates the transport type that was used for the replication connection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryTransportType"> </xref> opplistingsverdi som angir hvilken transport som ble brukt for replication-tilkoblingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the update sequence number (USN) value for the last successful replication cycle.
trans-unit.target: Henter oppdateringen sekvens tall (USN) verdien for den siste vellykkede replikering syklusen.

trans-unit.source: The USN value for the last successful replication cycle.
trans-unit.target: USN-verdien for den siste vellykkede replikering syklusen.

trans-unit.source: If no replication succeeded, the value is zero.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen replikeringen er fullført, er verdien null.

trans-unit.source: Gets the update sequence number (USN) of the last object update that was received.
trans-unit.target: Henter sekvensnummer for oppdatering (USN) for den siste oppdateringen for objektet som ble mottatt.

trans-unit.source: The USN of the last update that was received.
trans-unit.target: USN for den siste oppdateringen som ble mottatt.
